java.io.Closeable
public class KeyLookup
extends IdempotentCloser

Maintains a key lookup system from the ChunkReader and backing ChannelBuffer to the offset of the key in the channel buffer.

Field Detail

KEY_SIZE

public static int KEY_SIZE
Number of bytes needed to store a key in memory. This is used so that we can predict how much additional memory will be needed to store just the pointer data.
